README
======

Notes
-----
* This is SnapSync version 0.1 for Ubuntu.
* Proper installation depends on upstart.

Installation instructions
-------------------------
$ cd snapsync/
$ ./install.sh
The installation script will ask for a root password.
After installation, refresh the snapcode page and you should be ready to go.

Removal instructions
--------------------
$ cd snapsync/
$ ./remove.sh

Happy coding!
